<div id="review_1494838176" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1494838176" />
    <a title="Alex Boyd" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/12555211-alex-boyd"><img alt="Alex Boyd" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1346875114p2/12555211.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1494838176?book_show_action=true">Jan 04, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Alex Boyd" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Alex Boyd" href="/user/show/12555211-alex-boyd">Alex Boyd</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1494838176" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10519393250970468605">This is a really dense essay, and Tolkien has a habit of following intellectual rabbit trails. If you don&apos;t mind taking a long time to read a short piece, it is definitely worth the effort. He discusses not only the history, purpose and misconceptions of fairy tales, he also discusses with great passion and importance how they relate to the nature and soul of man. </span>
  <span id="freeText10519393250970468605" style="display:none">This is a really dense essay, and Tolkien has a habit of following intellectual rabbit trails. If you don't mind taking a long time to read a short piece, it is definitely worth the effort. He discusses not only the history, purpose and misconceptions of fairy tales, he also discusses with great passion and importance how they relate to the nature and soul of man. </span>
  <a data-text-id="10519393250970468605" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


