        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2197795658" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15074529107729842804">I mean I&apos;m a Tolkienite so of course I&apos;m going to rate this five stars. He&apos;s intake on faerie stories is amazing. Tolkien was such a gift to this world and I can never get tired from his work.</span>
  <span id="freeText15074529107729842804" style="display:none">I mean I'm a Tolkienite so of course I'm going to rate this five stars. He's intake on faerie stories is amazing. Tolkien was such a gift to this world and I can never get tired from his work.</span>
