<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/36229073-the-flame-imperishable"><img alt="The Flame Imperishable: Tolkien, St. Thomas, and the Metaphysics of Faërie" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1514580227l/36229073._SX98_.jpg" />
